      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it waxed and the interior spotless. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Feel free to ask any questions, I\u2019m happy to chat!",
