      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, exhibiting a level of preservation that satisfies the most exacting standards. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a history of fastidious care and climate-controlled storage. For the discerning enthusiast seeking a turn-key acquisition of the highest order, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class. We invite serious inquiries to inspect this flawless example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 44900.0,
