    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited for whoever gets to take this beauty home. It has been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
