    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe, rod bearing replacement, and a recent valve adjustment to factory specifications. The suspension geometry remains precise with refreshed bushings and original dampers. The exterior finish exhibits exceptional depth with no evidence of clear coat failure or panel misalignment. Interior Nappa leather bolsters are firm, and all pixel displays remain sharp. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the serious enthusiast.",
